<head>FUNERAL GIFT</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">治喪禮物</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>GIFT GIVEN to the DEAD WHEN these are being BURIED.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>HUMAN AFFAIRS 57.</p>
<p>賻，送喪家治喪用的錢財、布帛和車馬，主要指錢財。</p>
<p>賵，送與死者的車馬，用以陪葬。後泛指助喪之物。</p>
<p>“ 襚 ” ，贈予死者的衣被。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
